  "description": "Blacklist mods to prevent players from joining with those mods installed.",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <img alt=\"Blacklister Logo\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/avatars/1342/75/638872366672495232.png\" width=256 height=256>\n  <h1>Blacklister</h1>\n</div>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/project/blacklister\">\n<img alt=\"Modrinth\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=000000&color=00AF5C\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/blacklister\">\n<img alt=\"CurseForge\"\n  src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=000000&color=F16436\">\n</a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/etWwCMDGFH\">\n    <img alt=\"Discord\"\n      src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=000000&color=5865F2\">\n    </a>\n    </p>\n\n## Features\nBlacklister allows server owners to blacklist certain mods in the configuration file, preventing any player except operators to join if they have one of those mods installed.\n\n## Configuration\nThe configuration file is located at `config/Blacklister/config/configuration.toml`\n\n### Need more?\nFeel free to request features on the Discord server.\n\n",
